<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Newsteter, uns hat fürgelegt Jacob Topler,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz ir im sein armleute czu Hengsfelt,
                                <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan> den
                            <expan>Chuncze<ex>n</ex></expan> Walczen und Beczolt Pfeiffer, gefangen
                        und in ir habe <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt.
                            <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., daz ir
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> armleute ledig lassen und in
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir habe, die ir in
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armleute<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>cze sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wil ew
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex>leute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add> helffen,
                            <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des ermant wirdt; und lat uns des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen bey
                            <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in vigilia
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Jacobi.</ab>
</div>
